snippet.title: Hitman: Blood Money - Reprisal - Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Hitman: Blood Money - Reprisal will be available on iOS and Android on November 30, 2023. Watch the latest trailer for Hitman: Blood Money - Reprisal to see gameplay from this upcoming action game, and get ready to take on the role of infamous contract killer Agent 47.

#IGN #Gaming #Hitman
